variables.description: The key name of the tag. You can specify a value that is 1 to 128 Unicode                   characters in length and cannot be prefixed with aws:. You can use                   any of the following characters: the set of Unicode letters, digits, whitespace,                      _, ., /, =, +,                   and -.
variables.name: Key

variables.description: The value for the tag. You can specify a value that is 1 to 128 Unicode                   characters in length and cannot be prefixed with aws:. You can use                   any of the following characters: the set of Unicode letters, digits, whitespace,                      _, ., /, =, +,                   and -.
variables.name: Value
